### Fetch a user
# @name getUser
@host = https://api.example.test
@userId = 42
GET {{host}}/v1/users/{{userId}}?expand=profile HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json
X-Client-Name: mark-fixture
?locale=fr-FR
&emoji=🚀

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
X-Request-Id: req-basic-001

{
  "id": 42,
  "name": "Zoë 東京",
  "active": true,
  "symbols": ["λ", "🚀"]
}

